  "title": "Business Development Executive (Freight Forwarding / 5 days)",
  "description": "<ul>\n  <li>Identify and develop new business opportunities in freight forwarding (air, sea, and land)</li>\n  <li>Build and maintain strong relationships with clients</li>\n  <li>Prepare and follow up on quotations and proposals</li>\n  <li>Work closely with the operations team to ensure smooth service delivery</li>\n  <li>Meet sales targets and provide regular sales reports</li>\n  <li>Stay updated on market trends and competitor activities</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Prior experience in freight forwarding or logistics sales preferred</li>\n  <li>Strong communication and negotiation skills</li>\n  <li>Able to work independently and as part of a team</li>\n  <li>Self-motivated and goal-oriented</li>\n</ul>\n<p>We regret only shortlisted candidates will be contacted. All applications will be handled confidentially. By submitting your application, you agree to the collection, use, retention, and disclosure of your personal information to prospective employers.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Wecruit Pte Ltd</p>\n<p>EA License No: 20C0270</p>",
